     =========================================================
     Geant4 - an Object-Oriented Toolkit for Simulation in HEP
     =========================================================

                            Test23
                            ------

This is a test program for checking cut per material as well as 
a sample for store/retrieve physics table.
 

In this test, two boxes with the same material but different 
cut values are defined. In one event, two particles with same 
energy are generated and each will be tracked in different box.   
Here is a output of /run/particle/dumpCutValues command.

============= The cut Energy ==============================
                            gamma              e-    
Cut in range       
                Air           1 mm            1 mm 
               Air'           1 mm            1 mm 
                 Al           1 mm            1 mm 
                Al'           1 cm            1 cm 
                 Pb           1 mm            1 mm 
                Pb'           1 mm            1 mm 
Cut in energy
                Air         990 eV          990 eV 
               Air'         990 eV          990 eV 
                 Al        6.89 keV         597 keV
                Al'        20.5 keV        4.55 MeV
                 Pb         101 keV        1.38 MeV
                Pb'         101 keV        1.38 MeV
===================================================
 